Na-Kel Allah Smith (amụrụ na Julaị 22, 1994) bụ onye America na-agba skateboard, rapper, ónyé na-ede egwu na onye na-eme ihe nkírí. Na mbụ, ọ bụ onye na-agba skateboard si n'ógbè Los Angeles, a maara ya màkà mmekọrịta ya na ndị otu hip hop Odd Future, na-apụta na vidiyo egwu, vlogs na ihe ngosi TV Adult Swim Loiter Squad, ma na-eme ihe nkiri na ndị otu ya.
Smith malitere ọrụ egwu ya n'afọ 2013, na-egosi amaokwu mbụ ya edere na Tyler, abọm studio nke abụọ nke Onye Okike Wolf na "Trashwang"

N'afọ 2014, mgbè ọ pụtara na vidiyo kachasị elu "Cherry", Smith guzobere ụlọ ọrụ ngwaike / uwe nke ya, Hardies, ya na onye otu ya bụ Tyshawn Jones. N'afọ 2015, o guzobere Hog Slaughta Boyz, duo nke Smith na ónyé bụbu ónyé otu Odd Future bụ Earl Sweatshirt mejupụtara. N'afọ 2018, Smith pụtara na ihe nkiri azụmahịa mbụ ya, Mid90s, nke Jonah Hill duziri. N'afọ 2019, Smith wepụtara abọm studio mbụ ya bụ Twothousand Nakteen site na A Dream No Longer Deferred Records na Narcowave
